<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>Welcome to ImpactDev!</title>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				background-color: #f5f5f5;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				color: #333;
			}
			.container {
				max-width: 600px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 20px;
				background-color: #fff;
				border-radius: 8px;
				box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			}
			.header {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			.logo {
				max-width: 100px;
				height: auto;
			}
			.message {
				font-size: 16px;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			.cta-button {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 10px 20px;
				background-color: #007bff;
				color: #fff;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 4px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="header">
				<img class="logo" src="https://www.example.com/logo.png" alt="ImpactDev Logo">
				<h1>Welcome to ImpactDev!</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="message">
				<p>Dear
					{{ user.firstName }},</p>
				<p>Welcome to the ImpactDev family! Your account is now ready for use.</p>
				<p>Access our platform at
					<a href="http://localhost:5173">www.impactdev.com/leaves-mangement</a>
					to manage leaves and availability.</p>
				<p>You can also update your password directly within the platform.</p>
				<p>If you have any queries, contact our support team at
					<a href="mailto:support@example.com">Support Email Address</a>.</p>
				<p>Exciting times ahead!</p>
				<p>Best regards,</p>
				<p>ImpactDev Team</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
